extends layout

block content
  h1(style='clear:both;') Most loved:
    br(style='clear:both;')
    br

    - each val, favour in langsLoved
      div(style='float:left;width:20%')
        p(style='font-style:italic;overflow:auto') Most #{favour}d
    p(style='clear:both;')

    - each val, favour in langsLoved
      div(style='float:left;width:20%')
        - each lang in val
          p(style='white-space:pre;') #{lang.name} #{Math.round(lang.score*100)/100}

  hr(style='clear:both;')


  h1(style='clear:both;') Most well-known:
